Richard Anconina https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Anconina 0 Richard Anconina (French: [ʁi.ʃaʁ ɑ̃.kɔ.ni.na] ; born 28 January 1953) is a French actor. He won the César Award for Best Supporting Actor in 1983 and in 1989 was named César for Best Actor. Richard_Anconina ( French : [_ʁi.ʃaʁ_ɑ̃.kɔ.ni.na_] ; born_28_January_1953 ) is a_French_actor .
